<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.2.9">
<l>intu vārcaṭai yīcaṉaip payantanāṉ mukaṉai<supplied>t</supplied>taṉ ṉeḻilārum</l>
<l>unti māmalar mīmicaip paṭaittava ṉukantiṉi tuṟaikōyil</l>
<l>kunti vāḻaiyiṉ koḻuṅkaṉi nukarntutaṉ kuruḷaiyait taḻuvippōy</l>
<l>manti māmpaṇai mēlvaiku nāṅkūr vaṇpuru ṭōttamamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The temple where dwells sweetly rejoicing the one who created,</l>
<l rend="indent">on the top of a large flower in his beautiful navel,</l>
<l>The four-faced one who [then] produced Īśa with the moon</l>
<l rend="indent">in his long matted locks,</l>
<l>Is Vaṉpuruṭōttamam in Nānkūr where a mother monkey,</l>
<l rend="indent">having squatted, eating the fat fruit of a banana [tree],</l>
<l>Goes embracing her young and rests on a mango branch.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
